metadata.name: CHECKZ
metadata.description:
**CHECKZ by Sara "Sparky" Baumann in collaboration with Jake Baumann**

Everyone is notable. They are handing these things out like candy. 

Timed Open Edition mint available through 2/13/2023 @ 2:00 PM CST.  Mint if it sparks joy.

This is purely art and commentary on the moment. Please enjoy it for that.  There is no promise of value.
